      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine, delivering exceptional throttle response through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for precise power delivery. Mechanically robust, the double VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a critical structural point\u2014has been professionally reinforced to maintain lateral rigidity. While the aesthetic condition shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers. This is a visceral, analog machine engineered for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and chassis feedback.",
